features.name: Metallophos,SbcD_C SbcCD cleaves DNA hairpin structures. These structures can inhibit DNA replication and are intermediates in certain DNA recombination reactions. The complex acts as a 3'- 5' double strand exonuclease that can open hairpins. It also has a 5' single-strand endonuclease activity
